steps.instruction:
### Prep 
- Finely grate the ginger 


### Steps
1. Preheat oven to 425F
2. Line baking sheet with foil
3. Arrange shrimp in a single layer on baking sheet
4. Squeeze orange for juice (about 1/2 cup)
5. Combine in a medium saucepan the juice, soy sauce, rice vinegar, marmalade, sriracha, ginger,  and 1/4 cup of the green onions
6. Bring to a boil on medium high heat, cook for 1 minute
7. Remove from heat 
8. Pour sauce into a large bowl 
9. Stir in the remaining 1/4 cup of green onions 
10. Add shrimp to the sauce and coat
